parameters:
Would you like to watch the event? Volunteer for the
religious organization.

\nc<Senpai>We've received a dispatch request from the logistics
company.

\nc<Senpai>At least this time, it doesn't seem like there will be any
fighting over who gets to go. It's going to be a dispatch of
the entire team.

\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>(That's a relief♬ I was getting anxious since it was about
time for a dispatch, but if it's the logistics company, I
can relax.)
\nc<Senpai>No, I have work left to do, so I'll pass. Take care.

\nc<Senpai>Since it's a dispatch of the entire team, make sure not to
make any mistakes, okay?
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>A sudden dispatch of everyone... What are we going to do?

\nc<Member>Normally, they call us for big events or something like
that.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Well, if they're summoning succubi, that's only natural.

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>(I had Saki check last time... but I'm still concerned.
There's also work left to do as the team leader.)
